    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Yoton Clan, Level 4+</p><p>Earthen chakra runs through your veins, as you learn to balance the hardened nature release within. <br />You gain the following benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Increase your Intelligence or Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20. </p><p><br />• Select one damage type from the following; Wind, Earth or Water. <br />Your Calcified Skin clan feature now applied to the selected damage type. <br />You cannot change this once selected. </p><p><br />• Yoton clan jutsu you cast has their range increased by 10 feet. If the jutsu affects a line, cube, radius, sphere or cylinder, then increase its size by 10 feet</p><p><br />• You are immune to Environmental conditions and hazardous traps related to Fire or Heat.</p>",
